{
  "description": "An aerial view captures a complex of buildings, predominantly constructed in varied architectural styles, suggesting a university campus. The structures range from low-rise brick buildings with classic detailing to modern, multi-story concrete and glass designs.  A notable element is a large, horseshoe-shaped stadium with vibrant yellow seating, clearly visible on the left side of the frame. The buildings are arranged densely, with a mix of flat and gabled roofs, and interconnected walkways and courtyards.  Mature trees punctuate the landscape, providing greenery amidst the built environment.  The color palette is muted, dominated by beige, grey, and terracotta, with touches of blue from a tennis court visible between buildings.  The sky is overcast, providing soft, diffused lighting.",
